@startuml
title Control plane - detail

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

[ModelControlService] as ModelControl
[ModelCatalog] as Catalog
[ModelUploader] as Uploader
[ModelLifecycle] as Lifecycle
[AutoRollbackPolicyManager] as PolicyManager
[AutoRollbackMonitor] as RollbackMonitor
[AutoRollbackEvaluator] as RollbackEvaluator
[ModelRegistry] as Registry
[ActiveModelStateStore] as ActiveState
[ArtifactInspectorRegistry] as Inspectors
[WorkerRuntime] as WorkerRuntime
[ObservabilityRecorder] as Recorder

ModelControl --> Catalog
ModelControl --> Uploader
ModelControl --> Lifecycle
ModelControl --> PolicyManager

Catalog --> Registry
Catalog --> ActiveState
Catalog --> WorkerRuntime

Uploader --> Registry
Uploader --> Inspectors
Uploader --> Lifecycle
Uploader --> Recorder

Lifecycle --> Registry
Lifecycle --> ActiveState
Lifecycle --> WorkerRuntime
Lifecycle --> Recorder

PolicyManager --> Registry
PolicyManager --> ActiveState
PolicyManager --> Recorder

RollbackMonitor --> RollbackEvaluator
RollbackMonitor --> Recorder
RollbackEvaluator --> Lifecycle
RollbackEvaluator --> ActiveState
RollbackEvaluator --> Registry
RollbackEvaluator --> Recorder

note bottom of RollbackMonitor
  Monitor is event-driven:
  observability facts trigger policy evaluation.
end note

@enduml
